  "title": "Retail Associate (Jewel | Changi)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position: Retail Associate/ Assistant</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Location: Changi Airport / Jewel</strong></li><li>Working Days: 5days work week</li><li>Working Timing: shift work 6am - 12am</li><li>Transport will be provided for first and last Shift.</li><li>Starting Salary: $2200 - $2500+ Commission</li></ul><p>Interested applicants can also send your resume to WA:+65 8839 3566 (Ms Angel)  and allow our Consultant to match you with our Clients. </p><p>No Charges will be incurred by Candidates for any service rendered.</p><p><strong>The Role:</strong></p><ul><li>Reporting to the Operation Manager.</li><li>Managing day-to-day store operations.</li><li>Delivering an exceptional in-store experience to customers.</li><li>Achieving monthly sales targets</li><li>Promote and demonstrate to tourist & walk-in.</li><li>Handle customer inquiries and explain product benefits effectively.</li><li>Manage the POS system, payments, and cash handling.</li><li>Oversee in-store inventory and conduct regular stock checks.</li><li>Coordinate with the back-end office on sales matters.</li><li>Address customer feedback and provide excellent after-sales service.</li><li>Conduct customer satisfaction surveys and follow-ups.</li><li>Maintain accurate daily sales records.</li><li>Ensure the store is clean and well-organized.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties assigned by management.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>GCE 'O' Level with at least 1- <strong>2 years</strong> of retail experience</li><li>Able to commit to <strong>shift work</strong> <strong>retail hours</strong>, including <strong>weekends & public holidays</strong>.</li></ul><p></p><p>LIEW ONN KEE REG NO : R22108518</p><p>THE SUPREME HR ADVISORY EA NO:14C7279 </p>",
